<p><strong>Delivery layer in practice:</strong> Delivery-triggered post-purchase messaging and cross-sell timing accuracy for bulky home goods. For home goods stores, Cross-sell fires on `delivered` event, not `ordered`. Assembly instruction email at delivery +1 day before review ask. White-glove delivery mentions in cart hesitation for applicable SKUs. The failure mode to watch: Assembly frustration email before product arrives; review request pre-delivery on furniture. Monthly operator test: Cross-sell revenue timestamped after delivery event in reporting.</p>
<p><strong>Proof layer in practice:</strong> Assembly, comfort, and room photo reviews in browse and post-purchase. For home goods stores, Photo reviews for bulky SKUs in browse email two. The failure mode to watch: Text-only reviews insufficient for furniture consideration. Monthly operator test: Return rate down on email-influenced bulky SKUs.</p>
<p><strong>Analytics layer in practice:</strong> Room completion rate, cross-sell revenue, margin after shipping promos, browse window. For home goods stores, Project completion = multiple category purchases within 120 days. The failure mode to watch: Revenue without shipping subsidy margin. Monthly operator test: Contribution margin on email orders monthly.</p>
<p><strong>Deploying the Small decor scenario:</strong> Privy seasonal popup → Sequenzy post-purchase and seasonal → Omnisend cart → Yotpo reviews. Document trigger, delay, branch, and suppression rows before launch. Reconcile Shopify net sales weekly — platform attribution will overstate if popup, cart, and SMS discounts stack on the same session.</p>
<p><strong>Deploying the Furniture focus scenario:</strong> Justuno room quiz → Klaviyo segments → Sequenzy room series → Drip cross-sell → Postscript high-AOV cart SMS. Document trigger, delay, branch, and suppression rows before launch. Reconcile Shopify net sales weekly — platform attribution will overstate if popup, cart, and SMS discounts stack on the same session.</p>
<p><strong>Deploying the Omnichannel home scenario:</strong> AfterShip delivery triggers → Sequenzy cross-sell → Marsello VIP for room completers → Klaviyo reporting. Document trigger, delay, branch, and suppression rows before launch. Reconcile Shopify net sales weekly — platform attribution will overstate if popup, cart, and SMS discounts stack on the same session.</p>
<h2>Quarterly stack audit for home goods stores</h2>
<p><strong>Week 1 review:</strong> Room and style tag audit. Map delivery data source. Catalog top 20 SKUs by margin. Confirm collision calendar updated for upcoming peak weeks and that subscription, wholesale, or gift-buyer tags still suppress conflicting promos.</p>
